{"article_id":"NLnUrXnSZEdtiEgE","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Russian government spokesman Dmitry Peskov","depth":8},{"id":1,"text":"( L ) ,","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"pictured here with Russian President Vladimir Putin ,","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"said Monday ,","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"`` Such measures can make the world more dangerous , \"","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"in response to news","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"that the U.S. would abandon the Intermediate-Range Nuclear Forces Treaty .","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"|","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"Alexei Nikolsky , Sputnik , Kremlin Pool","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"Photo via AP Defense","depth":4},{"id":10,"text":"Kremlin :","depth":4},{"id":11,"text":"Russia will 'restore balance ' with new missiles","depth":5},{"id":12,"text":"if U.S. pulls out of treaty","depth":5},{"id":13,"text":"A Kremlin spokesman said Monday","depth":5},{"id":14,"text":"that Russia would retaliate","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"by developing new missiles `` to restore balance '' of military power","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"if the United States pulls out of a Cold War-era missile treaty .","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"President Donald Trump said on Saturday","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"the U.S. would abandon the Intermediate-Range Nuclear Forces Treaty ,","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"accusing Russia of breaching the agreement ,","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"which bans land-based , mid-range missiles .","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"\" It means that the United States is not disguising ,","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"but is openly starting to develop these systems in the future ,","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"and","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"if these systems are being developed ,","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"then actions are necessary from other countries , in this case Russia ,","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"to restore balance in this sphere , \"","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"Russian government spokesman Dmitry Peskov said Monday ,","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"according to Reuters .","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"\" This is a question of strategic security .","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"Such measures can make the world more dangerous , \"","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"Peskov also said ,","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"according to the Reuters report .","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"Morning Defense newsletter","depth":3},{"id":34,"text":"Sign up for Morning Defense , a daily briefing on Washington 's national security apparatus .","depth":4},{"id":35,"text":"Email Sign Up","depth":5},{"id":36,"text":"By signing up","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"you agree to receive email newsletters or alerts from .","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"You can unsubscribe at any time .","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"This site is protected by reCAPTCHA","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"and the Google Privacy Policy and Terms of Service apply .","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"Terminating the treaty ,","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"enacted by President Ronald Reagan and Soviet leader Mikhail Gorbachev in 1987 ,","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"would raise the possibility of an escalating arms race at a time","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"when Russia 's military has grown increasingly aggressive in its region .","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"Russia has has denied claims","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"that it violated the treaty","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"and accused the U.S. of undermining the agreement .","depth":6},{"id":48,"text":"Peskov said","depth":5},{"id":49,"text":"Moscow expects a detailed explanation from Washington on its withdrawal decision .","depth":5},{"id":50,"text":"Trump ' s national security adviser John Bolton is expected to meet with senior officials in Moscow on Monday","depth":4},{"id":51,"text":"and meet with Russian President Vladimir Putin on Tuesday .","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":103,"left":84,"right":102,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":84,"left":61,"right":83,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":61,"l